---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../../components/HeroSection.astro';
import CenteredTextBlock from '../../components/CenteredTextBlock.astro';
import FaqSection from '../../components/FaqSection.astro';
import FaqItem from '../../components/FaqItem.astro';
import TestimonialSlideshow from '../../components/TestimonialSlideshow.astro';

const reviewIds = ['c83dba55', 'fcb52150', '94fe245a'];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Design Guide - DJ Misha"
  description="Design guide page demonstrating reusable page components"
  bodyClass="landing"
>
  <Navigation />

  <HeroSection
    backgroundImage="/images/banner.jpg"
    alt="Wedding DJ in San Diego"
  >
    <h1 slot="tagline">Wedding DJ in San Diego</h1>
    <p slot="subTagline">The Perfect Soundtrack for Your Special Day</p>
  </HeroSection>

  <CenteredTextBlock>
    <h2>The Perfect Soundtrack for Your Special Day</h2>
    <p>
      Think about the most fun wedding you've attended. What do you remember?
      There's a good chance your time on the dance floor stands out. The music
      was pumping; the atmosphere was electric; and every song seemed to capture
      the essence of the couple's love story. That's the kind of unforgettable
      experience DJ Misha strives to create.
    </p>
    <p>
      The music is one of the most important parts of the reception, and with DJ
      Misha, it's not just about playing track after track — it's about creating
      a seamless blend of music that enhances the overall atmosphere of the
      night. He works closely with every couple to design the perfect live DJ
      set, making their wedding a dance party that creates lasting memories for
      years to come.
    </p>
    <p>
      <strong
        >Your wedding is about you. Let's make the music match your vision.</strong
      >
    </p>
  </CenteredTextBlock>

  <FaqSection>
    <FaqItem question="Can a Wedding DJ Take Song Requests?">
      <p>
        Absolutely, and the decision is entirely up to you. Your DJ is available
        to take requests if that is something you would like. Sometimes,
        requests can provide useful feedback from the audience and add a fun,
        interactive element to the party. However, our primary commitment is to
        you. The DJ will always prioritize your vision and the seamless flow of
        the musical journey we've planned together, ensuring any request fits
        the atmosphere and never disrupts the energy on the dance floor.
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="What Questions Should I Ask My Wedding DJ?">
      <p>
        Before hiring a wedding DJ, you'll want to ask certain questions to make
        sure they meet your needs for your special day. Here are some helpful
        questions to consider: What is your experience with DJ-ing weddings? How
        many have you done? Do you have testimonials from past clients? Do you
        have backup equipment in case of technical issues? How do you handle
        song requests and do-not-play lists? Can you make announcements during
        the event? Do you offer additional services? What is your policy on
        overtime? Is there an additional charge? How far in advance should we
        book your services? What is your cancellation or rescheduling policy?
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="How Many Hours Does a DJ Play at a Wedding?">
      <p>
        Our DJ services can be used throughout the entirety of your wedding day,
        from before the ceremony to the end of the reception. Our wedding
        package typically includes 4 hours of reception music. Custom packages
        can be created based on your individual needs.
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
    <FaqItem question="Does DJ Misha Perform at Destination Weddings?">
      <p>
        Yes! DJ Misha is available for national and international travel.
        Whether you're in San Diego or hosting a destination wedding in a unique
        location, he can bring the music to you. Reach out to us with details
        like your wedding location and date, because travel to any destination
        is possible. For destination weddings, DJ Misha will take care of all
        travel booking and equipment rentals that are required for a remote
        performance, ensuring there is no additional work for you. He will also
        handle all the coordination between vendors and event planners too,
        making your destination wedding planning an easy and efficient process.
      </p>
    </FaqItem>
  </FaqSection>

  <TestimonialSlideshow reviewIds={reviewIds} />

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
